event.description:
Casa Kitchen, Kolkata’s most popular Pure Vegetarian was formulated more than 5-years back with the concept of 'Go-Green' for the discerned. The delicious culinary offerings in North Indian, Continental and Oriental fares has enticed many queries at our end urging Casa Kitchen to reach out to them with our expertise for all their events and functions. 
In-keeping with the demand of our honoured epicure, we have formalized a set of interesting Menu that caters well to the palates of the Vegetarian lovers over a spread in North Indian – Punjabi, Rajasthani and general cuisine to Italian, Oriental and Continental items of favourite choices..to close an even with lip-smacking desserts and patisserie items in pure vegetarian combination. Be it straight from the Chaffing Dish or a Live Counter, our culinary experts will make every guests’ culinary event extremely memorable and impeccable. The prices range from Rs. 1250/- upwards till Rs. 3250/- plus taxes offering variety of Cuisine's.
